Author: sadrgnoises
Text: Your lists sound a lot like my past year and a half too, almost down to the bullet. I would definitely try to find yourself a therapist and see where to go from here. I also think admitting to yourself whether or not you think you have one is a step in the proper direction too.  I ended up reaching out to a therapist a few days ago and plan on talking with her about the issues that are happening and it's like a big weight off of my shoulders, since that person is going to have a more objective look at the behaviors and emotions and say what they think (in their educated opinion). Perhaps that would help you too.
